data.description: Perfectly maintained by original owner in sought after Brookstone CC and truly move in ready. This home features 4 bedrooms, 3 baths upstairs and a bedroom, bath, rec room and tons of storage in the basement. The kitchen is open to the family room and also has a butlers pantry that leads you into the dining room making this a great home for entertaining. The formal living room with its high ceilings & platium windows could also function as a home office. Excellent schools and conveniently located to shopping.
